          style={{
            color: "var(--parchment-dim)",
            fontSize: "0.75rem",
            letterSpacing: "0.1em",
            textTransform: "uppercase",
            marginBottom: "0.5rem",
          }}
        >
          Theseus seasonal review · {DISCLOSURE_LABEL}
        </p>
        <h1
          style={{
            fontFamily: "'Cinzel', serif",
            color: "var(--gold)",
